<paragraph id="3340217A400C5F27FF50F8944D093F13" blockId="27.[162,778,1822,1905]" pageId="27" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis id="018BFD68400C5F27FF50F8944E443F51" box="[162,288,1822,1843]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="294">Etymology:</emphasis>
The name of this species is descriptive of the name of the locality in 
<collectingRegion id="F13BEF98400C5F27FE0AF8B64DC63F33" box="[504,674,1852,1874]" country="Mexico" name="Chiapas" pageId="27" pageNumber="294">Chiapas State</collectingRegion>
